<div id="content-area">

	<h2 class="niceBigBold">Target Marketing on Twitter</h2>

	<p class="niceBold">TwitHawk is a real time target marketing engine that will find people talking on Twitter now by your chosen topic and location, allowing you to really hit your target mid conversation with ease.</p>

	<p class="niceLight">TwitHawk periodically searches Twitter for you and generates a list of matches for you to respond to or ignore, at the interval you choose, from 15 minutes to one month, it's your call.</p>

	<p class="niceLight">Monitor your campaigns true CPC with onsite link tracking<br />
	(with a site average CPC of less than $0.02)<br />
	and Google Analytics integration.</p>
	
	<p class="nicelight">Never miss an opportunity on Twitter again</p>

	<div class="coolhr"></div>

	<ol id="signup-steps">
		<li>Sign up</li>
		<li>Setup your searches</li>
		<li>Get new followers or leads. Hawk Squawk!</li>
	</ol>

